  "title": "Faceted values",
  "body": "Just wondering if I am able to do this through a widget or something that is already built (new to this!)\r\n\r\nThe top section is a repeat of the second section. I want them to both to show the faceted values but the top section I want to link through to a different URL - so not act as a facet, but still show faceted values? And the URL to be generated from the category name and the current faceted values.\r\n\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/24576147/21203478/77d6360a-c2b7-11e6-8d10-07ae732949dc.png)\r\n",
